Usage: writeSdpFile [-help] -file <fileName> [-template  | -topGroup <topGroupName>] [-template  | -command ] [-template  | [-updateRelativePlaceConstraint  | -updateOrientation ]]

-help                              # Prints out the command usage
-command                           # dump command file (bool, optional)
-file <fileName>                   # file name (string, required)
-template                          # dump template file (bool, optional)
-topGroup <topGroupName>           # top group to be dumped (string, optional)
-updateOrientation                 # update orientation of sdp instances before
                                   # dumping them (bool, optional)
-updateRelativePlaceConstraint     # update relative place constraint of sdps
                                   # before dumping them (bool, optional)